  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 200 degrees C.",
    "Sprinkle chicken breasts with salt, pepper, and garlic cloves.",
    "Heat olive oil in a stone bowl (dolsot) over medium heat. Add chicken and cook for about 3 minutes per side or until golden brown.",
    "Add thyme and rosemary to the stone bowl. Place chicken on top of herbs.",
    "Place stone bowl in oven, close door, and bake for 20-25 minutes or until internal temperature reaches at least 74 degrees C (165 F).",
    "Remove from oven and let rest for 5 minutes before serving."
